    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "h",
      "content": [
        "2 John\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "toc1",
      "content": [
        "2 John\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "mt1",
      "content": [
        "2 John\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "chapter",
      "marker": "c",
      "number": "1",
      "sid": "2JN 1"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "s1",
      "content": [
        "A Greeting from the Elder\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "r",
      "content": [
        "(3 John 1:1–4)\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "m",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "1",
          "sid": "2JN 1:1"
        },
        "The elder, \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "m",
      "content": [
        "To the chosen lady and her children, whom I love in the truth—and not I alone, but also all who know the truth—\n",
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "2",
          "sid": "2JN 1:2"
        },
        "because of the truth that abides in us and will be with us forever: \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "m",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "3",
          "sid": "2JN 1:3"
        },
        "Grace, mercy, and peace from God the Father and from Jesus Christ, the Son of the Father, will be with us in truth and love. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "s1",
      "content": [
        "Walking in the Truth\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "r",
      "content": [
        "(John 8:30–47)\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "m",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "4",
          "sid": "2JN 1:4"
        },
        "I was overjoyed to find some of your children walking in the truth, just as the Father has commanded us. \n",
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "5",
          "sid": "2JN 1:5"
        },
        "And now I urge you, dear lady—not as a new commandment to you, but one we have had from the beginning—that we love one another. \n",
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "6",
          "sid": "2JN 1:6"
        },
        "And this is love, that we walk according to His commandments. This is the very commandment you have heard from the beginning, that you must walk in love. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "s1",
      "content": [
        "Beware of Deceivers\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "m",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "7",
          "sid": "2JN 1:7"
        },
        "For many deceivers have gone out into the world, refusing to confess the coming of Jesus Christ in the flesh. Any such person is the deceiver and the antichrist. \n",
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "8",
          "sid": "2JN 1:8"
        },
        "Watch yourselves, so that you do not lose what we have worked for,",
        {
          "type": "note",
          "marker": "f",
          "content": [
            " ",
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "fr",
              "content": [
                "1:8 "
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "ft",
              "content": [
                "NE and WH what you have worked for"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "caller": "+"
        },
        " but that you may be fully rewarded. \n",
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "9",
          "sid": "2JN 1:9"
        },
        "Anyone who runs ahead without remaining in the teaching of Christ does not have God. Whoever remains in His teaching has both the Father and the Son. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "m",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "10",
          "sid": "2JN 1:10"
        },
        "If anyone comes to you but does not bring this teaching, do not receive him into your home or even greet him. \n",
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "11",
          "sid": "2JN 1:11"
        },
        "Whoever greets such a person shares in his evil deeds. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "s1",
      "content": [
        "Conclusion\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "r",
      "content": [
        "(3 John 1:13–14)\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "m",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "12",
          "sid": "2JN 1:12"
        },
        "I have many things to write to you, but I would prefer not to do so with paper and ink. Instead, I hope to come and speak with you face to face,",
        {
          "type": "note",
          "marker": "f",
          "content": [
            " ",
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "fr",
              "content": [
                "1:12 "
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "ft",
              "content": [
                "Literally mouth to mouth"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "caller": "+"
        },
        " so that our joy may be complete. \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "b"
    },
    {
      "type": "para",
      "marker": "m",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "verse",
          "marker": "v",
          "number": "13",
          "sid": "2JN 1:13"
        },
        "The children of your elect sister send you greetings.",
        {
          "type": "note",
          "marker": "f",
          "content": [
            " ",
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "fr",
              "content": [
                "1:13 "
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "char",
              "marker": "ft",
              "content": [
                "BYZ and TR include Amen."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "caller": "+"
        },
        " "
      ]
    }
  ]
}